### 异步函数签名记录 ###

============================================================
函数：send_otp
============================================================
签名：async def send_otp(client: httpx.AsyncClient, phone: str) -> dict[str, Any]
输入：client (HTTP 客户端), phone (手机号)
输出：RPC 结果 dict
行为：规范化手机号后发送 OTP 验证码

============================================================
函数：register_handle
============================================================
签名：async def register_handle(client, config, phone, otp_code, handle, ...) -> DIDIdentity
输入：client, config, phone, otp_code, handle, invite_code?, name?, is_public?, services?
输出：DIDIdentity (包含 user_id 和 jwt_token)
行为：一站式 Handle 注册流程

============================================================
函数：recover_handle
============================================================
签名：async def recover_handle(client, config, phone, otp_code, handle, *, services?) -> tuple[DIDIdentity, dict]
输入：client, config, phone, otp_code, handle, services?
输出：(DIDIdentity, 恢复结果 dict)
行为：通过重新绑定到新 DID 来恢复 Handle

============================================================
函数：resolve_handle
============================================================
签名：async def resolve_handle(client: httpx.AsyncClient, handle: str) -> dict[str, Any]
输入：client, handle
输出：查找结果 dict (包含 handle, did, status)
行为：解析 Handle 到 DID 映射

============================================================
函数：lookup_handle
============================================================
签名：async def lookup_handle(client: httpx.AsyncClient, did: str) -> dict[str, Any]
输入：client, did
输出：查找结果 dict
行为：通过 DID 查找 Handle

